		"description": "<p>Your attack staggers your target, exposing it to follow-up attacks. If the target is one size category larger than you or smaller, it makes a Strength saving throw against your maneuver DC. On a failure, you deal your @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.vKckTQevhrZgeJJ9]{Favored Ordnance} damage and push the target a number of feet away from you equal to 5 + 5 for every 5 points it failed its saving throw by. In addition, the target is [[/condition id=rattled]] until the end of your next turn. While rattled, attack rolls against the target are made with advantage.</p>",
